 BNXN BNXN (Buju) has shared a teaser for his new single ‘Kenkele’ featuring Wande Coal.   The singer shared the song’s teaser on his Instagram on Sunday, 17th June 2022. He also added that ‘Kenkele’ is the first single off his “Bad Since ’97” EP scheduled for release in August. He captioned the teaser, “New music on Thursday!! Featuring my Faveee @wandecoal  “Bad Since ’97” EP out August  Tell a friend to tell a friend .” Watch the song’s teaser HERE:   A post shared by BNXN FKA BUJU (@toyourears)